title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Oct 12 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Oct 12 2022
description:
It's looking good for Clay on the Hunter Biden bet: CNN's Jake Tapper asks Biden about possible charges against his son Hunter, Biden makes sympathy plea, says Hunter has cleaned up his life and he's proud of him. Buck says, "I'm saving up for a house, Clay, let's not get too crazy with the cost of the steak in our bet." Biden tells Tapper he can beat Trump in 2024. Clay says, "Trump is the only reason Joe Biden would run again. I think Trump is the life vest around Joe Biden." Impaired John Fetterman needs teleprompter for NBC interview, journos silent. C&B say Fetterman is not physically capable of being a U.S. Senator. Draymond Green punches out teammate with no consequences.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
